text: Zachary Woods (born September 25, 1984) is an American actor and comedian. He is best known for his roles as Gabe Lewis for three seasons on the NBC sitcom The Office and as Jared Dunn on the HBO comedy series Silicon Valley. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Trenton, New Jersey Category:Comedians from New Jersey
